gomodel:SYNGO_413  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099059 replaced by GO:0048787" , "Rationale: Average enrichment of Neuronal membrane glycoprotein M6-a in docked synaptic vesicles is >4.3 fold (Table S1).\nEnriched in glutamatergic vs. GABAergic terminals about 3.3 fold (Table S5). Experimental description: To isolate docking complexes from rat brain, we first prepared synaptosomes and subjected them to limited proteolysis to dissociate pre- and postsynaptic membranes (Figure 1A). p. 286" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9880-1214" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9681-3318" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9377-7414" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0269-0311" ;
